reviewText:
These short stories are still fun after nearly 50 years, they take me back to my childhood and Sunday afternoon when the program aired in the UK. The quality and colour is good fo a program of this age. I am sure that children today will enjoy, and be inspired by the adventures of The Forest Rangers.

Charles Forsyth

An excellent show.
Brings back memories of the show when it was originally broadcast on the CBC in the
early sixties.
